```rust
fn touch_mutably<A: Asset>(mut assets: ResMut<Assets<A>>) {
    for _ in assets.iter_mut() {}
}
```

## What went wrong

Frequency that i can `touch_mutably` per second decreases rapidly

## Investigation

The following issues already report this or something similar 
* #2439
* #16586
* #18808
* #18882

